OL,7,FElsewhere, he called for a #20 a week
OL,8,Fincrease to child benefit, which the
OL,9,Fparty claims would take 60,000
OL,10,Fchildren out of poverty, for powers
OL,11,Fover policing to be handed to the
OL,12,FSenedd, and for Wales to have "greater
OL,13,Fpowers over migration", including
OL,14,FWales-specific visa schemes.
