OL,7,FHe said: "As an internationalist
OL,8,Fparty, unlike Labour and the Tories we
OL,9,Fin Plaid Cymru are not afraid to call
OL,10,Fout the disastrous consequences of
OL,11,Fsevering ties with the world's largest
OL,12,Ftrading bloc.
OL,14,F"We have been clear, consistent and
OL,15,Funequivocal in recent years that
