OL,9,Fap Iorwerth, who was appointed Plaid
OL,10,Fleader 12 months ago.
OL,12,F"Firstly, fair funding for Wales.
OL,13,FPlaid Cymru is the only party
OL,14,Fadvocating for the abolition of the
OL,15,FBarnett formula which has seen Wales
OL,16,Flose out to the tune of billions of
OL,17,Fpounds now over the years.
