OL,7,FThe Barnett Formula, first introduced
OL,8,Fahead of the 1979 General Election, is
OL,9,Fused by the UK Treasury to calculate
OL,10,Fthe annual block grants for the Welsh
OL,11,Fand Scottish governments, and the
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland executive. It
OL,13,Fdetermines the overall funding
OL,14,Favailable for public services like
OL,15,Fhealthcare and education in the
OL,16,Fdevolved nations.
