OL,7,FMr ap Iorwerth said that scrapping the
OL,8,Fformula in favour of a needs-based
OL,9,Fmodel was "essential if we want to be
OL,10,Fable to adequately fund our public
OL,11,Fservices" and that it should be the
OL,12,F"bare minimum" of what the next UK
OL,13,FGovernment offers Wales.
OL,15,FHe criticised the UK Treasury's
OL,16,Fdecision to class the HS2 high-speed
OL,17,Frail project as an "England and Wales"
OL,18,Fscheme despite the route being
OL,19,Fentirely in England ` meaning Wales
OL,20,Fhad lost out on billions in funding.
