OL,7,FBecause it was classed as England and
OL,8,FWales, the project did not trigger the
OL,9,Fmechanism which would normally see
OL,10,Fextra funding given to the devolved
OL,11,Fnation.
OL,13,FThe Plaid Cymru leader said: "Because
OL,14,Fit's classed as an England and Wales
OL,15,Fproject, Scotland and Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fare compensated. But there's not a
OL,17,Fsingle mile, a single inch of HS2
OL,18,Ftrack in Wales and we get nothing.
