OL,7,FMr ap Iorwerth says the party will
OL,8,Fdemand a "fair funding system for
OL,9,FWales, based around our needs".
OL,11,FThe manifesto outlines the party's
OL,12,Fcalls for funding Westminster which
OL,13,Fwould give the Welsh Parliament the
OL,14,Fpower to make more decisions about
OL,15,Fwhat happens here.
OL,17,FThe party leader said: "We will
OL,18,Faddress the cost-of-living crisis and
OL,19,Fprovide Welsh solutions to Welsh
OL,20,Fproblems."
